{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8dce77c9ff","title":"反对党的领导干部的右派言论","origin":"《右派言论集》（河南医学院马列主义教研室编印，1958年4月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"176a72cf16","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"8dce77c9ff"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"00d8e3d85b","name":"河南医学院"},{"id":"0fa9a87bbb","name":"卢鹏"},{"id":"a61f8f95b0","name":"宁文俞"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2837bcb6a5","type":"title","text":"反对党的领导干部的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8dce77c9ff"},{"id":"bc6ab64b2b","type":"authors","text":"河南医学院卢鹏宁文俞","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8dce77c9ff"},{"id":"70dcb162bd","type":"subtitle","text":"(卢鹏：河南医学院外科基础教研组助教；宁文俞：工会文化教员)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8dce77c9ff"},{"id":"f800d17b13","type":"paragraph","text":"学校“四大金刚八大台柱”都是杀人不见血的东西。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8dce77c9ff"},{"id":"3feae5b55b","type":"paragraph","text":"我的肉体在毛泽东照耀下，我的精神却在卢长山压榨下，程耀吾来后是换汤不换药。(卢鹏)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8dce77c9ff"},{"id":"8d84262832","type":"paragraph","text":"卢长山盲目无知，不学无术，藉党的领导作威作福，他不配作高等学校的领导。(宁文俞)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8dce77c9ff"},{"id":"d1ae5e91f6","type":"paragraph","text":"程耀吾你残杀青年，残害过我，解放前我背了四年红包袱，解放后我背了九年黑包袱。(卢鹏)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8dce77c9ff"},{"id":"07716df446","type":"paragraph","text":"我一定要把卢专山赶出河南医学院，要使程耀吾在群众压力下深刻受到教育，将“四大金刚八大台柱”压下去。也不主张把他们赶出去，全国30多所高等学校都把他们赶出去谁来搞工作？让他们留下来当教员。(卢鹏)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8dce77c9ff"}],"page":{"id":"de8a581020","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8dce77c9ff","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}